Kesan buruk apa?

22
00:01:17,697 --> 00:01:19,187
Awak cakap bukan-bukan.

23
00:01:19,212 --> 00:01:21,273
Oh Tuhan! Awak mesti tarik...

24
00:01:21,298 --> 00:01:23,013
