Saya...

153
00:08:12,912 --> 00:08:14,213
Saya rasa ia hebat.

154
00:08:14,304 --> 00:08:17,427
Sejujurnya, saya sangat ingin tahu.

155
00:08:18,712 --> 00:08:20,715
Awak kata awak suka melukis.

156
00:08:22,099 --> 00:08:24,310
Jadi, kenapa awak tak buat
apa yang awak suka?

157
00:08:29,206 --> 00:08:31,103
Hanya yang terpilih...

158
00:08:31,313 --> 00:08:33,591
